### Quick Start - Docker (Preview the UI)

If you want to **preview the chat UI**, use Docker. Only requires Docker installed.

**Step 1: Clone and Navigate**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/McK-Internal/citizen-dev5.git
cd citizen-dev5/deployer-apps/citizen-dev5/src
```

**Step 2: Run with Docker**
```bash
./scripts/docker-dev.sh
```

Open http://localhost:3000 in your browser.

