### Optional: Embed a Chatbot in Your Webapp

If you want the agents to actually respond to messages (not just preview the UI), you'll need AI Gateway credentials:

```bash
cat > .env << 'EOF'
AI_GATEWAY_INSTANCE_ID=your_instance_id
AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=your_api_key
EOF
```

Get credentials from [Platform McKinsey → AI Gateway](https://platform.mckinsey.com). This connects your app to LLMs (GPT, Claude, etc.) through McKinsey's enterprise gateway.

